Win32 Service Kit Build Instructions
------------------------------------

Materials
---------

Windows95 or WindowsNT computer.

Metrowerks CodeWarrior Pro 1 for Windows

"ALS Prolog Support" folder installed in {Compiler f}..\
	(contains alspi.h and alspro.dll.lib)

Abobe FrameMaker 5.0

Adobe Acrobat 3.0


Instructions
------------

1) Build Executables
	Open Service_Kit_Project.mcp in CW Pro 1.
	Build "Service Test" Target.
	Build "Service Package Stub" Target.

2) Build Manual
	Open Win32_Service_Kit.frame in FrameMaker 5.0
	Print to a Postscript file.
	Convert Postscript file to PDF with Acrobat 3.0

3) Construct Distribution Package
	Create a folder called "Win32 Service Kit" plus the version number,
	with the following files in it (remove underscores where necessary):
		Service Test.exe
		Service Package Stub.exe
		Win32 Service.pro
		Simple Service.pro
		Win32 Service Kit.pdf
